Eleanor Hunt https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eleanor_Hunt 0 Eleanor Hunt (January 10, 1910 – June 12, 1981) was an American film actress. She starred opposite John Wayne in the 1934 Blue Steel. She was married to actor Rex Lease and George Hirliman, with whom she adopted Georgelle Hirliman as an infant. Eleanor_Hunt ( January_10_,_1910 – June_12 , 1981 ) was an_American_film_actress .
